    <MoneyCTABox store="BabySam" affiliateUrl="https://to.babyworld.se/t/t?a=1945556825&as=2065068845&t=2&tk=1&cupa_sku=0d8c0970-c98e-4186-8416-4b6609446e5d&url=https://www.babysam.se/bugaboo-fox-5-renew-barnvagn-moon-grey-graphite-onesize" />

    <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-6">2. Nuna Mixx Next, bäst allround</h2>
